Located on the popular Upton St and within close proximity to JB Hifi, The Good Guys and many other bulky goods retailers, this 235sqm showroom plus office is now available to lease.

The property features:

• 164sqm showroom
• 71sqm mezzanine office
• Large glass entrance door
• High clearance ceiling
• Bathroom and Kitchenette
• Zoned Fringe Business Precinct

Price: $98,000.00 per annum Including Outgoings + GST

For further information and inspections on the property contact your marketing agents CBRE today.
